---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title={"한줄코딩 - About"}>
  <main
    class="min-h-[60vh] max-w-[calc(100%-2rem)] flex flex-col justify-center items-center mx-auto text-[rgb(var(--foreground))] text-lg leading-relaxed m-4 sm:m-4"
  >
    <h1 class="font-['DungGeunMo'] text-5xl sm:text-6xl mt-4 mb-8 sm:mb-12 text-center">
      <span>About</span>
    </h1>
    <div
      class="text-center text-gray-800 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-white shadow-2xl rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 w-full max-w-2xl space-y-8"
    >
      <section>
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">한줄코딩이란?</p>
        <p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">매일매일 한 줄 씩, 꾸준한 개발을 하자는 뜻.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          작은 한 줄이 쌓여 큰 프로젝트가 되듯, 멈추지 않는 성장을 지향합니다.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700" />

      <section>
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">무엇을 다루나요?</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white space-y-1">
          <li>개발자 · 비개발자 모두를 위한 IT 이야기</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700" />

      <section>
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">함께해요</p>
        <p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          최신 소식은 <a href="/news" class="text-sky-500 hover:underline">News</a>에서 확인하세요.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/6lueparr0t"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block mt-6 px-5 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 dark:border-white text-gray-900 dark:text-white hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-white dark:hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
        >
          개발자 GitHub 바로가기 →
        </a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
